reviewText: I love the video, but the audio sounds like a (a.m.)radio
REAL SHOW MAY J AS A REAL PERSON

Loved the interviews & live performances Mary does here. Plus it has the actual music videos as extras. If you're only a casual Mary fan you might not like the interviews but if you're a diehard fan, this DVD is for you! Highly Recommended!

I have all her albums and dvd's had to add this one to the collection. If you are a die hard fan this is a must have.
Thanks Mary!
A gift for my cousin she loves her some Mary J. Blige she's going to the concert here in Memphis; and this was an early birthday gift. Thank you amazon.com for once coming through again.
